%S A113933 0,-1,1,2,2,2,-1,16,28,6,30,6,130,-1,255,6795,2670,1006
%N A113933 a(n) is the least k such that 2^2^n + 1 - 10^k = A000215(n) - 10^k is a (positive) prime, or -1 if no such k exists.
%e A113933 F5 - 10^2 = 4294967197 is prime.
%o A113933 (PARI) a(n) = my(x=2^2^n); for(k=0, oo, if(ispseudoprime(x), return(k)); x-=9*10^k; if(x<=0, return(-1))) \\ _Jianing Song_, May 14 2026
%Y A113933 Cf. A000215.
%K A113933 sign,hard,more,less
